OL,6,FA meeting of the Executive is set to
OL,7,Ftake place on Thursday amid an ongoing
OL,8,Fdispute with the UK Government over
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland's finances.
OL,11,FAt this first substantive meeting of
OL,12,Fthe newly-formed Executive, Ministers
OL,13,Fwill tackle the pressing issues of
OL,14,Ffinance and childcare.
OL,16,FEarlier this week the Government
OL,17,Foutlined the details of a #3.3bn
OL,18,Ffunding package - but said locally-
OL,19,Felected ministers . The parties have
OL,20,Fsaid they did not agree to revenue-
OL,21,Fraising measures.
