OL,6,FFirst Minister Michelle O'Neill and
OL,7,FDeputy First Minister Emma Little-
OL,8,FPengelly have ruled out a 15 percent
OL,9,Frates hike.
OL,11,FAhead of Thursday's meeting, Ms
OL,12,FO'Neill said they hope "to be at the
OL,13,FTreasury's door" in the coming days,
OL,14,Fand said they always knew it would be
OL,15,Fa "battle a day".
