OL,6,FThere is currently no free childcare
OL,7,Fprovision in Northern Ireland, and
OL,8,Fparents say they are being left behind
OL,9,Fas elsewhere in UK families benefit
OL,10,Ffrom more support measures.
OL,12,FThe Assembly debated a Sinn Fein
OL,13,Fmotion calling for Executive to work
OL,14,Fcollectively to deliver a strategy to
OL,15,Fmake high quality childcare affordable
OL,16,Ffor families as a priority.
OL,18,FEducation Minister Paul Givan has
OL,19,Frevealed that a fully 'up-and-running
OL,20,Fchildcare strategy' .
