OL,6,FMore money is also needed to upgrade
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland's public services and
OL,8,Ffacilitate public sector pay awards
OL,9,Fand there is a limit to how far the
OL,10,Fnewly-formed Executive's finances will
OL,11,Fstretch.
OL,13,FThe First Minister has maintained that
OL,14,Fit is not about Northern Ireland
OL,15,Fhaving "a begging bowl approach" or
OL,16,Ffailing to recognise that efficiencies
OL,17,Fcan be made.
