OL,6,F"I think on the one hand for it to be
OL,7,Frecognised that we are under funded,
OL,8,Fand on the other hand to say we need
OL,9,Fto burden households who are really
OL,10,Fstruggling right now with further
OL,11,Fcosts is not acceptable", she said.
OL,13,FThe multi-million pound question
OL,14,Fremains how to resolve the unfinished
OL,15,Fbusiness of revenue raising amid
OL,16,Fcompeting priorities across the board.
OL,17,FUpdates to follow.
